      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The mechanical condition is robust, with a recently performed valve adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis benefits from upgraded suspension components that sharpen turn-in while maintaining the car's legendary balance. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car that perfectly bridges the gap between raw analog feedback and modern performance capability.",
