      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss luster, having been regularly waxed and garaged. Upon close inspection, you may find a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips on the hood, which are typical for its age but do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all buttons and switches retaining their original tactile feel. Mechanically, this car is in great shape; the engine idles smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and replaced the cabin air filter. All electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. This car comes with a clean title and a documented service history, ensuring you can drive away with confidence.",
